Dock Panel Suite Control C# Visual Studio 2012 Design Look

Update 2.05.2013: The modifications of this project are merged with the newest build of Dock Panel Suite. For more information on Dock Panel Suite 3.0 and its current state look here.

This control is an editted and extended version of the original Dock Panel Suite Control from SourceForge. Several more classes have been changed beyond the usual Skin classes in the original project to provide a more Visual Studio 2012 genuine look.

The current version is based on version 2.5 RC1 of Dock Panel Suite. This is not the most current state of the Control which has been actively developed here.
